data.description: Fresh Full exterior paint!! This home offers OWNED solar panels for the lowest electric bills! Inside you will see a formal dining/living room, an oversized family room, gourmet kitchen with a double ovens, built-in microwave, granite counters with an oversized island, extra kitchen cabinet space with butlers pantry. The master suite includes a deluxe bath with two walk-in closets & an oversized laundry room with extra cabinet space. Home was just painted inside. Backyard is fully landscaped with a fenced pet area on one side and grass, plants, trees, & a lovely garden with fruits & vegetables such as oranges, lemons, seedless limes, serrano peppers & more!
